products.title: Herbstlicher Tigerwelpe
products.description: Dies ist eine fotorealistische Nahaufnahme eines süßen Tigerwelpen, der auf seinem Rücken liegt und spielt, vor einem Hitzschlag des herbstlichen Goldes. Das Detail der Felltextur und das glänzende Licht in seinen Augen heben die Natürlichkeit hervor, perfekt gedruckt auf 170 GSM Semi-Glossy-Prints mit dem höchsten Standard. Mit einem haltbaren Kiefernholzrahmen in Schwarz ist dieses Bild bereit, an der Wand gehängt zu werden. Der Künstler wollte eine süße, friedliche und herzerwärmende Atmosphäre schaffen, die einladend wirkt. Eine minimalistische Komposition mit viel Negativraum und maximal zwei Tieren sorgt für eine friedliche Ausstrahlung.

products.title: Galactic Resonance
products.description: Experience the peaceful and meditative mood in this hyperrealistic digital matte painting. A high plateau with rock formations that point to a majestic night sky. Illuminated by soft moonlight, the vibrant purple and magenta tones of the galaxy spring to life against the vast expanse of sky. The photorealistic textures, the natural lighting, and the finely resolved stars and planets create a believable and awe-inspiring view. The artist's intention was to depict the tranquility and infinite beauty of the universe, both captivating and mesmerizing at the same time. The finest quality of this piece is guaranteed with an 8k resolution, optimized for large print formats in rooms and is impressive from both distance and up close. Proudly printed on 170 gsm (65 lb) Semi-glossy and includes a hanging kit. The piece is perfectly framed with durable black pine wood. Suitable not only as a home dÃ©cor, but an immersive, visual experience.

products.title: Golden Nebula
products.description: Immerse yourself in the ethereal beauty of 'Golden Nebula', a masterpiece capturing an enchanting misty forest on a floating mountain with a starry sky peeking through the treetops. The dramatic cloud formations cast over the serene landscape are perfectly reflected, creating both visual and emotional depth. Enhanced with every leaf, stone, and water droplet distinctly visible, owing to its 8K ultra-high-definition quality that ensures a room-filling, photorealistic experience. Printed on 170 gsm (65 lb) semi-glossy paper, the quality you can feel. Enclosed in a durable black pine wood frame. The artist's intention was to encapsulate the world's untouched yet breathtaking splendour.
